We have also come to consider ourselves something of an expert in all things dog, and so we will answer any questions you have about dogs when you book a consultation. We will even do it for free! We believe that there is a great deal of satisfaction in doing one thing and doing it well, knowing that it will make pets satisfied and owners happy. It makes all the hard work and loud barks and constant obsessing over the tiniest changes worth it. The satisfaction of your pet is our reward! That is why we know just dogs.
